doc.after: Tunnel Vision was written by Justin Timberlake Timothy Timbaland Mosley Jerome J Roc Harmon and James Fauntleroy and produced by Timbaland Timberlake and Harmon Timberlake arranged and produced his vocals which were recorded at Larabee Studios in North Hollywood California Other instrumentalists were Harmon on keyboards and Elliot Ives on guitar The song was engineered by Chris Godbey assisted by Alejandro Baima and mixed by Jimmy Douglass Godbey and Timberlake at Larabee Studios 1
